{"tid":1627931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（長片慎入）2019.10.03.大圍市中心：當晚追捕、對罵、舉旗經過","createTime":"2019-10-05T19:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:40:48.000Z","uid":50275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f27797bdb1ddb3bf34e712c5a020119ebecfa98f","tid":1627931,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"（長片慎入）<br />\n2019.10.03.大圍市中心：當晚追捕、對罵、舉旗經過<br />\n[12:23am]<br />\n<br />\n0:00 現場人群與警對罵<br />\n0:19 防暴警忽然衝前追捕<br />\n0:23 「呢度呀...呢度呀...」<br />\n1:02 一青年被捕，倒地<br />\n1:09 警員以胡椒噴槍指嚇記者，不斷要記者後退<br />\n2:20 少女不滿朋友被捕尖叫，表示只是街坊、食高宵夜<br />\n3:26 有社工展示證件，希望協助被捕人士，警員叫他走開，「唔好阻差辦公」<br />\n4:01 （長槍上膛聲）圍觀群眾增多，警員忽然替長槍上彈<br />\n4:09 現場人群大叫「放人」，警員後退<br />\n6:39 現場人群與警對罵，警：「收皮啦」<br />\n6:51 屋苑閘內居民阿姨追罵警員，叫佢地走<br />\n9:51 警員退至馬路，舉黑旗<br />\n10:35 警登車離開<br />\n12:36 疑有人向警車投擲物件，警下車<br />\n13:23 向行人天橋瞄準<br />\n15:15（上膛聲）再次瞄準，上膛<br />\n16:24 警：「夠薑落黎啦」幾位警員對街大罵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gjbOySPCoGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgjbOySPCoGk&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=6397c70a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gjbOySPCoGk</a>"},{"pid":"05ae8070acc365633a5c171746a32ce98f846e07","tid":1627931,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAm4rSj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAm4rSj.png&h=141c9784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpKJHqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpKJHqP.png&h=cc002478&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"718a2c7c8780587eb970d8ca493bf58595dd6ff7","tid":1627931,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}